igh-Taylor (R-T)\ninstability, and the large density-gradient-scale length helps to reduce the\nR-T growth rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Nov 2015 07:25:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-07"}
